---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Catalyst Neuromorphic" description="Building neuromorphic processors to challenge the way intelligence is computed." hasFog={true}>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="v2-hero" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v2-col">
      <p class="v2-label reveal">About</p>
      <h1 class="v2-hero-h1 reveal">AI has a hardware problem.</h1>
      <p class="v2-hero-sub reveal">We're building the processors to fix it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
  <section class="v2-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v2-col">
      <h2 class="v2-h2 reveal">The scaling wall</h2>

      <p class="v2-body reveal">Modern AI runs on hardware that was never designed for intelligence. GPUs burn hundreds of watts per chip. Data centres already consume over 2% of global electricity, and that share is climbing fast. Training a single large language model can use more energy than a hundred homes do in a year. The models are getting bigger, but the returns are shrinking.</p>

      <p class="v2-body reveal">And for all that power, these systems still can't learn from new information without being retrained from scratch. They can't run without a data centre. They can't operate without sending your data to someone else's infrastructure.</p>

      <div class="v2-pullquote reveal">
        <p>The human brain does all of this on 20 watts.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="v2-body reveal">It learns continuously. It processes information in real-time. It runs at the edge, on-device, with no internet connection required. The gap between biological intelligence and artificial intelligence isn't a software problem. It's a hardware problem.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE'RE BUILDING -->
  <section class="v2-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v2-col">
      <h2 class="v2-h2 reveal">Neuromorphic processors</h2>

      <p class="v2-body reveal">Neuromorphic chips compute the way neurons do. They're event-driven &mdash; they only consume energy when there's something to process. They can learn on the hardware itself, not just run pre-trained models. They operate at the edge, on-device, without cloud dependency. And they do it at a fraction of the power cost.</p>

      <p class="v2-body reveal">This technology exists. Intel has Loihi. IBM built TrueNorth. But both are closed, corporate, and inaccessible. If you're not inside those companies or their select research programmes, you don't get access. The hardware that could reshape computing is locked behind walls.</p>

      <div class="v2-pullquote reveal">
        <p>We're not asking for permission to compete with billion-dollar companies. We're just doing it.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="v2-body reveal">Catalyst is building the open alternative. Full processor designs, published research, and a cloud platform anyone can use today.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHERE WE ARE -->
  <section class="v2-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v2-col">
      <h2 class="v2-h2 reveal">Where we are</h2>

      <p class="v2-body reveal">We're early. Two processor generations are designed, built in software, and validated on real hardware. Both have published papers you can read today. A cloud API is live &mdash; you can run a neuromorphic network right now, without buying anything.</p>

      <p class="v2-body reveal">We're raising funding and building toward manufactured silicon. That's the goal: a physical chip you can hold, running real neuromorphic intelligence. We're not there yet. But the architecture is complete, tested, and protected by patent.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOUNDER -->
  <section class="v2-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v2-col">
      <p class="v2-body reveal">Catalyst was started by <strong class="v2-strong">Henry Shulayev Barnes</strong>, an engineering student at the University of Aberdeen. He started it because the neuromorphic hardware that should exist doesn't, and the hardware that does exist isn't accessible. He is currently a member of Techscaler, Scotland's tech startup community.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRUST -->
  <section class="v2-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v2-col">
      <h2 class="v2-h2 reveal">Don't take our word for it</h2>

      <p class="v2-body reveal"><a href="/research" class="v2-link">Read the papers.</a> Two published papers on Zenodo with DOIs. Open access. Every claim documented.</p>

      <p class="v2-body reveal"><a href="/cloud" class="v2-link">Try the cloud.</a> The API is live. Run a neuromorphic network from your terminal. Free tier available.</p>

      <p class="v2-body reveal"><a href="/research" class="v2-link">Check the hardware.</a> Our designs run on real FPGA boards, not just simulators. Physical silicon execution.</p>

      <p class="v2-body reveal"><a href="https://github.com/catalyst-neuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="v2-link">Join the community.</a> Open GitHub, public research, growing backers. We build in the open.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IP -->
  <section class="v2-section-sm" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v2-col">
      <div class="v2-ip reveal">
        <div class="v2-ip-row"><span class="v2-ip-label">UK Patents</span><span class="v2-ip-value">Filed February 2026</span></div>
        <div class="v2-ip-row"><span class="v2-ip-label">RTL</span><span class="v2-ip-value">BSL 1.1 &mdash; proprietary</span></div>
        <div class="v2-ip-row"><span class="v2-ip-label">SDK</span><span class="v2-ip-value">BSL 1.1</span></div>
        <div class="v2-ip-row"><span class="v2-ip-label">Papers</span><span class="v2-ip-value">Open access on Zenodo</span></div>
        <div class="v2-ip-row"><span class="v2-ip-label">API Client</span><span class="v2-ip-value">MIT &mdash; open source</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GET IN TOUCH -->
  <section class="connect-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,3.6rem); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.035em; line-height:1.08; text-align:center; margin-bottom:18px;">Get in touch.</h2>
    <p class="connect-email"><a href="mailto:henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com">henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com</a></p>
    <div class="connect-grid">
      <a href="https://github.com/catalyst-neuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.4 5.4 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65S8.93 17.38 9 18v4"/><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">GitHub</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Source &amp; contributions</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/research" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">Research</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Papers &amp; benchmarks</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style is:global>
    /* =============================================
       V2 — The Narrative (Notion/Browser Co style)
       ============================================= */

    /* Narrow reading column */
    .v2-col {
      max-width: 580px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 28px;
    }

    /* Hero */
    .v2-hero {
      padding: 180px 0 60px;
    }
    .v2-label {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.6);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .v2-hero-h1 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .v2-hero-sub {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      margin-top: 20px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* Sections — large whitespace between */
    .v2-section {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .v2-section-sm {
      padding: 40px 0 80px;
    }

    /* Section headings */
    .v2-h2 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.15;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    /* Body text — book-like */
    .v2-body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.38);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .v2-body:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .v2-strong {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Inline links */
    .v2-link {
      color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .v2-link:hover {
      color: #60A5FA;
    }

    /* Pull quotes */
    .v2-pullquote {
      margin: 48px 0;
      padding: 0 0 0 24px;
      border-left: 2px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.35);
    }
    .v2-pullquote p {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.7rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      font-style: italic;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    }

    /* IP table — simple rows */
    .v2-ip {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }
    .v2-ip-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      padding: 14px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    }
    .v2-ip-label {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    }
    .v2-ip-value {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .v2-hero { padding: 140px 0 48px; }
      .v2-section { padding: 56px 0; }
      .v2-col { padding: 0 20px; }
    }

    /* Connect section */
    .connect-section { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 32px 100px; }
    .connect-email { font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .connect-email a { color: rgba(59,130,246,0.8); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
    .connect-email a:hover { color: #60A5FA; }
    .connect-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .connect-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; padding: 36px 24px; border-radius: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #fff; background: linear-gradient(165deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 35%, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 100%); backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06); border: 1px solid transparent; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.45), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.14), inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.02); position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: box-shadow 0.5s, transform 0.3s; }
    .connect-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.55), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.18), inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
    .connect-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: 20px; padding: 1px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59,130,246,0.22) 0%, rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 25%, rgba(59,130,246,0.02) 50%, rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 75%, rgba(59,130,246,0.18) 100%); -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0); -webkit-mask-composite: xor; mask-composite: exclude; pointer-events: none; z-index: 5; opacity: 0.55; transition: opacity 0.4s; }
    .connect-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
    .connect-card svg { color: #60A5FA; margin-bottom: 16px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .connect-label { font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .connect-sub { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .connect-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  </style>

</BaseLayout>
